<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV46">
<l>maṭaneñca meṉṟun tamateṉṟu mōrkaru maṅkaruti</l>
<l>viṭaneñcai yuṟṟār viṭavō vamaiyumap poṉpeyarōṉ</l>
<l>ṟaṭaneñcaṅ kīṇṭa pirāṉār tamataṭik kīḻviṭappōyt</l>
<l>tiṭaneñca māyemmai nīttiṉṟu tāṟun tirikiṉṟatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who, thinking it an ignorant heart and thinking it their’s reflect upon [a course</l>
<l>of] action [and] experienced a heart to be sent off, are they content to let it go?</l>
<l>When we send [it] off under the feet of the lord, who tore the broad heart of that one with the name of gold,</l>
<l>it went as a strong heart, leaving us, [and] wanders until today.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
